{"type": "article", "id": 60580, "title": "一款低矮浑圆的台灯，灵感源自热气球｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-01-23T23:17:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 8581, "name": "Peca"}, {"id": 6781, "name": "Swarovski"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 45667, "name": "Deadgood"}, {"id": 56183, "name": "Kutarq Studio"}, {"id": 48920, "name": "Woud"}, {"id": 56184, "name": "James Tapscott"}, {"id": 33353, "name": "Magnus Long"}, {"id": 56185, "name": "Gala Wright"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190123195550muCFMp8gzjeU9hrb.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #3c3c3c; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #3c3c3c} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>PUMP TABLE LAMP by Kutarq Studio for Woud </h3><p>西班牙设计工作室 Kutarq Studio 为丹麦设计品牌 Woud 设计了一款名为 PUMP 的台灯，低矮浑圆的造型，非常适合放在搁架、桌面或是窗台上。</p><p>PUMP 的设计灵感源自热气球和灯笼。一个椭圆形的玻璃球体放在一个黑色的管状钢底座内，使其外观像灯笼一样悬浮在地面上。球体的蛋白石外观散发出柔和的光芒，营造出宜人的环境光。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195614lZk8szDtErOIcBag.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901231956140yDaKUGSginE7f2e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195615ux5pZgNyC27ojfVH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.428906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901231956162FEG5wWRlC1kLzcs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195616ux29DQFi75yncBjs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://kutarq.com/project/30\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kutarq Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Naked and Hug by Magnus Long and Gala Wright for Deadgood</h3><p>Deadgood 是英国一家现代家具制造商，最近他们推出了两款座椅：Naked 和 Hug。</p><p>Naked 由设计师 Magnus Long 和 Gala Wright 设计，采用简单的粉末涂层金属框架和可互换的橡木贴面或软垫座垫做成，可根据用户的特定需求定制座椅。这款时尚的堆叠式会议椅非常适合在教育、工作场所或接待空间使用，不使用时可堆叠至八层高。</p><p>它还有一个户外版本，穿孔细节不仅减轻了椅子的形状，还遵循人体的形状，保证支撑人体核心部位，突出舒适性，与其搭配的还有一款 Naked 桌，和户外椅子一样是穿孔结构，室内室外皆可使用。</p><p>Hug 包括扶手椅和休闲椅，胶合板外壳搭配 Lloyd Loom 材料，另提供橡木和软垫饰面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195745Zc6CAJ9bUK4Qgazp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901231957443r4cWFqLMejwoRkx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195744MpkOvGeWCnHbic2g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195745HSf09vCWLNAiBpDF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195746ogrEQC2SixlJ35n8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195746KetUrG3pLws2QTob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195746iQn0NgAD48qWvMEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195746iBz16bKNflVj843o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195747V4vaBJFjOWLKCXYD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195747bIVgPAwKXlsTSkJx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.deadgoodltd.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Deadgood</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>tangent by Nendo for Swarovski</h3><p>tangent 是日本设计工作室 Nendo 为施华洛世奇家居工作室设计的室内装饰系列，其主要构成元素是一系列立方形框架，以及样式不同的水晶圆盘和金属环。</p><p>所有的形状元素均是以最简化的方式相互固定和支撑，看上去犹如处在失衡的边缘。基于环形在位置、方向和尺寸上的变化，每件物品也被赋予了不同的功能，例如烛台、花瓶、托盘和镜子等。水晶材质的圆盘被巧妙地放置，以反射出花朵和蜡烛的影像。水晶圆盘分为两种款式：蓝色水晶被用于可反光的镜面框架，白色水晶则用于黑色的哑光框架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195911jU4agizJTx3oHEWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195911BaNyU7k3G5KM2xTj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195913WLXNYR8OFprc13gB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195913xnkOeYX1AvNyPL2w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195914aDRCjBpekcQKqOVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019012319591461Q5s4VviyDzTOgr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123195914FHDkr2b7dOiq1a5j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901231959147KwOv0sDBAYmR9bE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/tangent/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Arc ZERO by James Tapscott</h3><p>James Tapscott 的新艺术作品“Arc ZERO – 日蚀”目前正在深圳 BAY ART 艺术节展出。新作改编自他在日本 Alps 节的著名作品：一座佛寺前雾气和灯光环绕的桥。</p><p>这是一个非常有挑战性的感知体验，真正令人惊叹的、具有空间转变性的体验。借用小面积的灯光和水面，空间似乎毫无边际、像一个黑暗、无尽的实体。水面反射圆弧形成一个完整的圆形，空间虽然比周边环境更加昏暗，但看起来像是一个入口区域，作品像是悬挂在空间中的阴影而不仅仅是表面的影子。观赏者能够在反射面上行走，反射景象随着人走动产生的涟漪而变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901232000050DIxQJh5XZTdUnEq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200005GmMBLXKZisCPJ0RY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200005OZmytW3h0lVENLHr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901232000062OdbpZ4tFsHGfJm7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200006vIH7X0Z3N61DURVj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200006Ixqf4sDMCoSNz9kV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200007T2Rtn0OKbz4GUPAl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200007o6nGAEVOmKDCgUy1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://studio-jt.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">James Tapscott</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>RIMA &amp; VERSO &amp; PAUSA by Caterina Moretti for Peca</h3><p>墨西哥设计工作室 Peca 经常与瓜达拉哈拉当地的手工艺人和设计师合作推出家具、配饰及室内设计作品，杂糅了传统和创新元素，产品线很特别。工作室的首席设计师 Caterina Moretti 喜欢探索天然的材料、纹理和样式，她喜欢用意想不到的方式将自然元素带入室内，强化自己的设计风格。</p><p>Peca 最近的新品是与墨西哥的材料和技术专家一起创作的，整个系列包括 VERSO，RIMA 和 PAUSA 三款产品。</p><p>RIMA 手工书柜的灵感来自一首诗的韵律，椭圆形底座搭配山毛榉木的板条立面，质感优雅，为整体作品创作出和谐与平衡的感觉。VERSO 桌也是用榉木制成的，两个木条相交构成的桌子底座创造出有机感，搭配圆形桌面。PAUSA 是一款特别的纸镇，由玛瑙、黄铜和榉木三种材料制成，每种都有不同的质地。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200052HnOpk25fFRP7ZrvY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200054dZkSeW91Vhya8xrY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200054qBCUhpw47E63bTvl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200054Qg4kyKZT3v2pAPtS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200052VJXST6wHaspB4jhL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.727344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200055beXHl8ISdi32YJVQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.289063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190123200100hslwuQ4HrBRfon3q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497656\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.peca.com.mx/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peca</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}